author: @andyle5716
text:
Ah. The seasonal horror special ep in the 5th season of 1, 2, 3 IVE. Their variety shows are getting more chaotic, but that's what I love about IVE. Neomu usgyeo. 😂 I've said this a long time ago. The order of IVE being scaredy cats in order.
- Liznyang-i 
- Wony 
- Yujinie. Though she and Maknae could've been in equal third, she is a bit more scared than Maknae. 
- Maknae 
- Gaeul Sunbae, since I now know that she is kinda afraid of creepy crawlies, like little lizards or some insects. 
- Last, but not least, Kongsuni. Who still doesn't quite get scared easily over anything. But on the Lottie World special when IVE were riding a rode rollercoaster, Kongsuni was a bit scared. 
The first game they played, 007 was so hilarious. When Gaeul Sunbae got ganged up by Annyeongz, she just accepted her fate. In FoREIgner we trust. She got bitten first. Dang! Let's go Gaeul Sunbae! She MC in this ep. And in the end IVE did it. I'm looking forward to watching tomorrow's ep. LiMakz are the food critics. And Sentimentals and YoungLiz are in a team.
